President Muhammadu Buhari will address the nation Thursday morning. Presidential Spokesman, Femi Adesina disclosed this in a statement Wednesday night. According to Adesina, “President Muhammadu Buhari will make a national broadcast on Thursday, February 16, 2023 at 7 am. “Television, radio stations and other electronic media outlets are enjoined to hook up to the network services of the Nigerian Television Authority and Radio Nigeria for the broadcast,” the statement concludes.